        "body": "**Title:**\r\nFix mobile responsiveness for Netflix Clone\r\n\r\n**Description:**\r\nHi! 👋\r\n\r\nThis PR fixes the layout issues on small screens (viewport width < 768px) for the Netflix Clone V2 project. Changes include:\r\n\r\n- Stacked navbar and menu items for mobile view\r\n- Hero section text and buttons scaled for smaller screens\r\n- Movie grids automatically resize to prevent clutter\r\n- Footer centered on mobile devices\r\n\r\nNow the website looks clean and readable on phones and tablets.\r\n\r\n_Note: I’m new to open source, so any feedback is greatly appreciated! 😊_",
