        "body": "**Description:**\r\n**Hello** \r\n\r\nThis PR adds a footer section to the Author Page. Previously, the page did not have a footer, which made the design feel incomplete.\r\n\r\n**Changes Made:**\r\n\r\nAdded a footer at the bottom of the page.\r\n\r\nIncluded copyright text: © 2025 Authors Website. All Rights Reserved.\r\n\r\nAdded social media links for X, Facebook, and LinkedIn using PNG icons.\r\n\r\nStyled the footer so that text and icons are centered and icons have a hover effect.\r\n\r\n**Preview:**\r\n\r\nThe footer now appears at the bottom of the page.\r\n\r\nSocial media icons scale slightly when hovered, giving a nice interactive feel.\r\n\r\n**Notes:**\r\nI’m new to open source and contributing under Hacktoberfest .\r\nPlease review and let me know if any improvements are needed.\r\n\r\nThank you \r\n\r\n",
